svg.text: Microsoft 365 F1 does not include Windows
Limitations: ·No access to productivity servers ·No Outlook Desktop access
Microsoft 365 F3 includes Windows Enterprise E3 except for Autopatch, Long Term Servicing Channel (LTSC), and Microsoft Desktop Optimization Pack (MDOP) features

g.text: Microsoft 365 F5 includes Windows Enterprise E5

svg.text: Limitations: ·No access to productivity servers ·No Outlook Desktop access ·No Voicemail
FastTrack helps customers deploy Microsoft 365.Customers with 150+ eligible licenses can use FastTrack at no additional cost for the life of their subscription.
